text: == Events == * The Tower of London is built. * Philaretos Brachamios does not keep his claim to the Byzantine Empire after he becomes duke of Antioch. * August 7 - Battle of Mellrichstadt between Henry IV, Holy Roman Emperor and the German anti-king Rudolf of Swabia == Births == * King Alexander I of Scotland, Scottish royal (died 1124) * Constance of France, daughter of King Philip I of France (died 1118)
